title: SC EP:816 I Saw A Monster
itunes:title: SC EP:816 I Saw A Monster
description: Tonight I will be speaking to Darren and he will be sharing an encounter he had when he was 13 years old. Darren talks about finding a structure in the woods and this monster came from around the structure. Darren and his friends were about 30 feet away from the creature. Darren said "At the time I did not know what it was..."
